headline: Can AMD’s Rally Continue After a 58.6% Surge in the Past Month?
summary: If you are trying to decide what to do with Advanced Micro Devices stock, you are definitely not alone right now. The past few months have been a wild ride for AMD, giving investors plenty to cheer about. After a steady upward climb, the stock closed at $252.92, with a stunning 109.7% gain year-to-date and an eye-popping 58.6% pop just in the last month.
